---
/**
 * Home Page
 * Minimal approach with IBM Plex Sans body text, technical card, CRT effects
 */
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Button from '../components/Button.astro';
---

<Layout title="AnswerLayer">
  <div class="crt-screen hero-section">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6" style="max-width: 48rem;">

      <div class="technical-card crt-glow">
        <div class="title-box">
          <h1 class="home-title crt-text">
            Generative Semantic Layer
          </h1>
        </div>

        <p class="body-text crt-text" style="margin-bottom: 1.25rem;">
          AnswerLayer generates a semantic layer from your database. Connect a data warehouse—PostgreSQL, BigQuery, Snowflake, MySQL—and get a complete semantic model in minutes. Entities, metrics, dimensions, filters, and relationships are created automatically by analyzing your actual data, not just the schema.
        </p>

        <p class="body-text crt-text" style="margin-bottom: 1.25rem;">
          The generated layer is fully editable. Domain experts refine definitions, add business logic, and control what's exposed. No YAML to maintain. No manual configuration. The AI does the grunt work; you curate the result.
        </p>

        <p class="body-text crt-text">
          Runs in your cloud. VPC deployment is standard—data never leaves your infrastructure. PII detection flags sensitive columns before exposure. Query guardrails prevent runaway operations. Full audit trails for compliance.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <style>
    .hero-section {
      min-height: calc(100vh - 80px);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .title-box {
      border: none;
      border-bottom: 2px solid var(--color-navy-900);
      padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
      margin: -2rem -2.5rem 1.5rem -2.5rem;
      background: transparent;
    }
    .home-title {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      text-transform: none;
      margin: 0;
      color: #151c3f;
    }
    @media (min-width: 640px) {
      .home-title {
        white-space: nowrap;
      }
    }
    .body-text {
      font-family: 'IBM Plex Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
      font-size: 1.0625rem;
      color: #374151;
      line-height: 1.75;
    }
    .technical-card {
      background: transparent;
      border: 2px solid var(--color-navy-900);
      padding: 2rem 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      position: relative;
    }
    .technical-card::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: -6px;
      border: 1px solid var(--color-navy-300);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .crt-link {
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      color: var(--color-navy-900);
      text-decoration: none;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      transition: opacity 0.2s;
    }
    .crt-link:hover {
      opacity: 0.7;
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
